					<span>ROI Marketing Solutions Ltd has worked with NTQ Solutions to develop an online marketing application over the past 1 year. During this time, NTQ has demonstrated good technical and communication skills over different parts of the software development cycle such requirement gathers and development. I would not hesitate recommending NTQ.</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-4">
				<div class="customer-picture bg-blue">
				</div>
				<div class="customer-name text-center">
					<span>Yusuke Akinaga</span>
				</div>
				<div class="customer-position text-italic text-center">
					<span>Account Manager, ITSherpa - Japan</span>
				</div>
				<div class="customer-review paragraph text-justify">
					<span>NTQ helped us identify clear specifications for our project and carried out testing after implemetation. NTQ possessed high technological and communication skills while maintaining a very low mistake rate. When I have had technical problems NTQ are always there to give a helping hand and always propose alternative and unique ideas. I have never seen or heard of such a cooperative company.</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
